  "detailed_description": "[h]Zombie Slayer[/h]<br>Zombie Slayer is an immersive first person shooter where you survive against endless waves of zombies. Team up with friends or survive alone to try and reach new records! The waves get harder as you go, so how long can you last? Kill zombies, earn points, buy weapons, unlock new rooms, and survive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/a3ab4bfae8499dc78265ddca85a0e09f.avif?t=1614646840\" width=76 height=185 /></span><br><br>This game currently includes 2 unique maps and 16+ weapons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map 1: Outpost</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/5abb517c7fd17fc69bcdd9d0f7f11df4.avif?t=1614646840\" width=450 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map 2: Fortress</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/8b8d4ba4c7100d18222e108d040a9e18.avif?t=1614646840\" width=450 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/0645908b589a95628a1730a3aea6bdf5.avif?t=1614646840\" width=400 height=400 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2>Zombie Slayer VR is in it's earliest stages of Alpha, meaning many changes are expected to come. This includes:<br><br>In the next update, we plan on adding some buildable objects and melee weapons.<br><br>However, in the future we will add:<br>- New maps<br>- Gun customization<br>- New guns<br>- Extra abilities<br>- Zombie bosses<br>- Easter eggs<br>- Bug fixes",
  "about_the_game": "[h]Zombie Slayer[/h]<br>Zombie Slayer is an immersive first person shooter where you survive against endless waves of zombies. Team up with friends or survive alone to try and reach new records! The waves get harder as you go, so how long can you last? Kill zombies, earn points, buy weapons, unlock new rooms, and survive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/a3ab4bfae8499dc78265ddca85a0e09f.avif?t=1614646840\" width=76 height=185 /></span><br><br>This game currently includes 2 unique maps and 16+ weapons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map 1: Outpost</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/5abb517c7fd17fc69bcdd9d0f7f11df4.avif?t=1614646840\" width=450 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map 2: Fortress</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/8b8d4ba4c7100d18222e108d040a9e18.avif?t=1614646840\" width=450 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299890/extras/0645908b589a95628a1730a3aea6bdf5.avif?t=1614646840\" width=400 height=400 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2>Zombie Slayer VR is in it's earliest stages of Alpha, meaning many changes are expected to come. This includes:<br><br>In the next update, we plan on adding some buildable objects and melee weapons.<br><br>However, in the future we will add:<br>- New maps<br>- Gun customization<br>- New guns<br>- Extra abilities<br>- Zombie bosses<br>- Easter eggs<br>- Bug fixes",
